Subject: [PATCH v2 31/58] i386/tdx: Track mem_ptr for each firmware entry of TDVF
Date:   Fri, 18 Aug 2023 05:50:14 -0400
Message-Id: <20230818095041.1973309-32-xiaoyao.li@intel.com>
